    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving naturally aspirated engine remains crisp, delivering linear power through its 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis integrity is solid, with a recently inspected rear subframe and updated VANOS seals to ensure timing precision. It features the factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery out of corners. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a healthy compression profile and responsive individual throttle bodies. Riding on factory Style 67 wheels with fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, this E46 offers a pure analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
